**Professional Profile**
Nguyen Hoang Loc is an emerging talent in information technology, with 6 months of project-based experience as a Cross-Platform Mobile Developer and Web Developer. Loc designed and developed a cross-platform E-Learning app using Flutter, Firebase, and SQLite, featuring comprehensive course management and discussion forums. Additionally, Loc built a modern, responsive movie ticket booking website, demonstrating strong UI/UX focus and intuitive design.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Proficient in Dart, Flutter, Python, and C#. Possesses strong understanding of database technologies including Firebase, SQLite, and MySQL. Skilled in Object-Oriented Programming (OOP), REST API integration, and version control with Git/GitHub.

**Education & Certifications**
Currently pursuing a Software Engineering major within Information Technology at Ton Duc Thang University. Loc also holds a Cambridge PET - B1 CEFR English Certificate (2023), demonstrating English proficiency.